Jina yaha marna yaha iske siba ab jana kaha.....
ji chahe jab hamko avaj do ham he wahi ham the jaha
jina yaha ........................jana kaha.....
ye mera git jivan sangit kal bhi koi dihrayega hu hu hum hu hu hum
jag ko hasane behrupiya rup badal aayega
kal khel me ham ho na ho gardish me tare rahege sada
bhuloge tum bhulenge wo par ham tumhare rahenge sada..................
